---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4 skill-item" style="animation-delay: 0s;">
		<Icon icon="terminal-window" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Fullstack Development</h2>
		<p>From front-end development & design to server deployment I am confident in my abilities to successfully take on large scale development projects.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4 skill-item" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
		<Icon icon="trophy" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>QA Testing, End-User Training, & Documentation</h2>
		<p>Over the past 10 years I've had to develop end-user training materials and conduct walkthroughs translating technical jargon into easily understandable end-user documentation.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4 skill-item" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
		<Icon icon="strategy" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Financial data & technical analysis</h2>
		<p>I have many years of experience successfully navigating tumultuous financial markets by using data/technical analysis and many differrent strategies</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.box {
		
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-400);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: 1.5rem;
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 5rem;
			background-color:rgba(255 118 244 / 0.06)
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}

	.skill-item {
		opacity: 0;
		transform: translateY(20px);
		animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
	}

	@keyframes fadeInUp {
		from {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateY(20px);
		}
		to {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateY(0);
		}
	}
</style>
